text: Mosese Voka (born 7 June 1985) is a Fijian rugby player for Fijian Latui in Global Rapid Rugby and the Fijian national team. His primary position is back row. In August 2019 he was named in Fiji's squad for the 2019 Rugby World Cup. ==References== Category:1985 births Category:Living people Category:Fijian rugby union players Category:Rugby union flankers Category:Fiji international rugby union players
